setup:
  - ask if user want to switch default shell to zsh
  - do not assume ctafconf's sources are in .config/ctafconf

GUI:
  - install
  - component installation
  - update
  - use the same lib as setup
  - change env variable
  - add/mod/suppr alias
  - handle profile

zsh:
  - allow for automatic sourcing of a config file when entering a directory
    and finding a .zenv or .env
    this config file should set a variable that would be displayed in the prompt
    to remember the special behaviors of the shell

